      <Math mode="display" tex="\begin{split}&amp;\displaystyle-\frac{\hbar^{2}}{2m}\Delta u+\Big{(}\hbar\partial_%&#10;{t}S+eA^{0}+\frac{\hbar^{2}}{2m}|\nabla S|^{2}+\frac{e^{2}}{2mc^{2}}|\mathbf{A%&#10;}|^{2}-\frac{\hbar e}{mc}\nabla S\cdot\mathbf{A}\Big{)}u=W^{\prime}(u)\\&#10;&amp;\displaystyle\partial_{t}u^{2}+\frac{\hbar}{m}\nabla\cdot\left[\left(\nabla S%&#10;-\frac{e}{\hbar c}\mathbf{A}\right)u^{2}\right]=0\\&#10;&amp;\displaystyle\kappa(\partial_{1}A_{2}-\partial_{2}A_{1})=eu^{2}\\&#10;&amp;\displaystyle\kappa(\partial_{2}A_{0}-\partial_{0}A_{2})=\frac{e\hbar}{cm}%&#10;\left(\partial_{1}S+\frac{e}{\hbar c}A_{1}\right)u^{2}\\&#10;&amp;\displaystyle\kappa(\partial_{0}A_{1}-\partial_{1}A_{0})=\frac{e\hbar}{cm}%&#10;\left(\partial_{2}S+\frac{e}{\hbar c}A_{2}\right)u^{2}.\end{split}" text="(- (Planck-constant-over-2-pi ^ 2 / (2 * m)) * Delta * u) + ((Planck-constant-over-2-pi * (partial-differential _ t)@(S) + e * A ^ 0 + (Planck-constant-over-2-pi ^ 2 / (2 * m)) * (absolute-value@(nabla@(S))) ^ 2 + (e ^ 2 / (2 * m * c ^ 2)) * (absolute-value@(A)) ^ 2) - ((Planck-constant-over-2-pi * e) / (m * c)) * nabla@(S cdot A)) * u = W ^ prime * u * (partial-differential _ t)@(u ^ 2) + ((Planck-constant-over-2-pi / m) * nabla) cdot delimited-[]@((nabla@(S) - (e / (Planck-constant-over-2-pi * c)) * A) * u ^ 2) = 0 * kappa * ((partial-differential _ 1)@(A _ 2) - (partial-differential _ 2)@(A _ 1)) = e * u ^ 2 * kappa * ((partial-differential _ 2)@(A _ 0) - (partial-differential _ 0)@(A _ 2)) = ((e * Planck-constant-over-2-pi) / (c * m)) * ((partial-differential _ 1)@(S) + (e / (Planck-constant-over-2-pi * c)) * A _ 1) * u ^ 2 * kappa * ((partial-differential _ 0)@(A _ 1) - (partial-differential _ 1)@(A _ 0)) = ((e * Planck-constant-over-2-pi) / (c * m)) * ((partial-differential _ 2)@(S) + (e / (Planck-constant-over-2-pi * c)) * A _ 2) * u ^ 2" xml:id="S0.E12.m1">

  <para xml:id="p49">
    <equation labels="LABEL:+N'" xml:id="S0.E16">
      <tags>
        <tag>(16)</tag>
        <tag role="autoref">Equation 16</tag>
        <tag role="refnum">16</tag>
      </tags>
      <Math mode="display" tex="N^{\prime}(u)[u]=6\int_{\mathbb{R}^{2}}\frac{u^{2}(|x|)}{|x|^{2}}\Big{(}\frac{%&#10;1}{2\pi}\int_{B(0,|x|)}u^{2}(y)dy\Big{)}^{2}dx=6N(u)." text="N ^ prime * u * delimited-[]@(u) = 6 * (integral _ (R ^ 2))@(((u ^ 2 * absolute-value@(x)) / (absolute-value@(x)) ^ 2) * ((1 / (2 * pi)) * (integral _ (B * open-interval@(0, absolute-value@(x))))@(u ^ 2 * y * differential-d@(y))) ^ 2 * differential-d@(x)) = 6 * N * u" xml:id="S0.E16.m1">
        <XMath>
          <XMDual>

  <para xml:id="p64">
    <equation xml:id="S0.Ex54">
      <Math mode="display" tex="c_{n}:=\inf_{\gamma\in\Gamma_{n}}\max_{\sigma\in\mathbb{D}_{n}}\mathcal{I}(%&#10;\gamma(\sigma))\to+\infty\quad\hbox{as }n\to+\infty." text="formulae@(c _ n assign (infimum _ (gamma element-of Gamma _ n))@((maximum _ (sigma element-of D _ n))@(I) * gamma * sigma) to + infinity, [as ] * n to + infinity)" xml:id="S0.Ex54.m1">
        <XMath>
          <XMDual>
            <XMRef idref="S0.Ex54.m1.2"/>
            <XMWrap>
              <XMDual xml:id="S0.Ex54.m1.2">
                <XMApp>
                  <XMTok meaning="formulae"/>
                  <XMRef idref="S0.Ex54.m1.2.1"/>
                  <XMRef idref="S0.Ex54.m1.2.2"/>
                </XMApp>
                <XMWrap>
                  <XMApp xml:id="S0.Ex54.m1.2.1">
                    <XMTok meaning="multirelation"/>
                    <XMApp>

  <para xml:id="p67">
    <equation labels="LABEL:partialtheta" xml:id="S0.E19">
      <tags>
        <tag>(19)</tag>
        <tag role="autoref">Equation 19</tag>
        <tag role="refnum">19</tag>
      </tags>
      <Math mode="display" tex="\partial_{\theta}\tilde{\mathcal{J}}_{q}(\theta,u)=2qe^{4\theta}\varphi(qe^{4%&#10;\theta}N(u))N(u)+2q^{2}e^{8\theta}\varphi^{\prime}(qe^{4\theta}N(u))N^{2}(u)-2%&#10;e^{2\theta}\int_{\mathbb{R}^{2}}G(u)\,dx," text="(partial-differential _ theta)@((tilde@(J)) _ q) * open-interval@(theta, u) = (2 * q * e ^ (4 * theta) * varphi * q * e ^ (4 * theta) * N * u * N * u + 2 * q ^ 2 * e ^ (8 * theta) * varphi ^ prime * q * e ^ (4 * theta) * N * u * N ^ 2 * u) - 2 * e ^ (2 * theta) * (integral _ (R ^ 2))@(G * u * differential-d@(x))" xml:id="S0.E19.m1">
        <XMath>
          <XMDual>
            <XMRef idref="S0.E19.m1.8"/>
            <XMWrap>
              <XMApp xml:id="S0.E19.m1.8">
                <XMTok meaning="equals" role="RELOP">=</XMTok>
                <XMApp>
                  <XMTok meaning="times" role="MULOP">⁢</XMTok>
                  <XMApp>
                    <XMApp>
                      <XMTok role="SUBSCRIPTOP" scriptpos="post2"/>
                      <XMTok meaning="partial-differential" name="partial" role="OPERATOR">∂</XMTok>
                      <XMTok font="italic" fontsize="70%" name="theta" role="UNKNOWN">θ</XMTok>
                    </XMApp>
                    <XMApp>
                      <XMTok role="SUBSCRIPTOP" scriptpos="post2"/>
                      <XMApp>
                        <XMTok name="tilde" role="OVERACCENT" stretchy="false">~</XMTok>
                        <XMTok font="caligraphic" role="UNKNOWN">J</XMTok>
                      </XMApp>
                      <XMTok font="italic" fontsize="70%" role="UNKNOWN">q</XMTok>
                    </XMApp>
                  </XMApp>
                  <XMDual>
                    <XMApp>
                      <XMTok meaning="open-interval"/>
                      <XMRef idref="S0.E19.m1.1"/>
                      <XMRef idref="S0.E19.m1.2"/>

    <equation labels="LABEL:partialu" xml:id="S0.E20">
      <tags>
        <tag>(20)</tag>
        <tag role="autoref">Equation 20</tag>
        <tag role="refnum">20</tag>
      </tags>
      <Math mode="display" tex="\begin{split}\displaystyle\partial_{u}\tilde{\mathcal{J}}_{q}(\theta,u)[v]=&amp;%&#10;\displaystyle\int_{\mathbb{R}^{2}}\nabla u\nabla v\,dx+\frac{q^{2}}{2}e^{8%&#10;\theta}\varphi^{\prime}(qe^{4\theta}N(u))N(u)N^{\prime}(u)[v]\\&#10;&amp;\displaystyle+\frac{q}{2}e^{4\theta}\varphi(qe^{4\theta}N(u))N^{\prime}(u)[v]%&#10;-e^{2\theta}\int_{\mathbb{R}^{2}}g(u)v\,dx.\end{split}" text="(partial-differential _ u)@((tilde@(J)) _ q) * open-interval@(theta, u) * delimited-[]@(v) = ((integral _ (R ^ 2))@(nabla@(u) * nabla@(v * d * x)) + (q ^ 2 / 2) * e ^ (8 * theta) * varphi ^ prime * q * e ^ (4 * theta) * N * u * N * u * N ^ prime * u * delimited-[]@(v) + (q / 2) * e ^ (4 * theta) * varphi * q * e ^ (4 * theta) * N * u * N ^ prime * u * delimited-[]@(v)) - e ^ (2 * theta) * (integral _ (R ^ 2))@(g * u * v * differential-d@(x))" xml:id="S0.E20.m1">

    <equation labels="LABEL:assurdo" xml:id="S0.E21">
      <tags>
        <tag>(21)</tag>
        <tag role="autoref">Equation 21</tag>
        <tag role="refnum">21</tag>
      </tags>
      <Math mode="display" tex="\forall k\in\mathbb{N}^{*}\ \exists q_{k}\in(0,1/k)\ \hbox{s.t.}\ \forall h\in%&#10;{\mathbb{N}}\ \exists j_{k,h}{\geqslant}h:\|u^{(n,q_{k})}_{j_{k,h}}\|^{2}_{2}&gt;k." text="for-all@(k) element-of N ^ * * exists@(q _ k) element-of open-interval@(0, 1 / k) * [s.t.] * for-all@(h) element-of N * exists@(j _ (list@(k, h))) &gt;= h colon ((norm@((u ^ (open-interval@(n, q _ k))) _ j _ (list@(k, h)))) ^ 2) _ 2 &gt; k" xml:id="S0.E21.m1">
        <XMath>
          <XMDual>
            <XMRef idref="S0.E21.m1.8"/>
            <XMWrap>
              <XMApp xml:id="S0.E21.m1.8">
                <XMTok name="colon" role="METARELOP">:</XMTok>
                <XMApp>
                  <XMTok meaning="multirelation"/>
                  <XMApp>
                    <XMTok meaning="for-all" name="forall" role="BIGOP">∀</XMTok>
                    <XMTok font="italic" role="UNKNOWN">k</XMTok>
                  </XMApp>
                  <XMTok meaning="element-of" name="in" role="RELOP">∈</XMTok>
                  <XMApp>
                    <XMTok meaning="times" role="MULOP">⁢</XMTok>
                    <XMApp rpadding="5.0pt">
                      <XMTok role="SUPERSCRIPTOP" scriptpos="post2"/>
                      <XMTok font="blackboard" role="UNKNOWN">N</XMTok>
                      <XMTok fontsize="70%" meaning="times" role="MULOP">*</XMTok>
                    </XMApp>
                    <XMApp>
                      <XMTok meaning="exists" role="BIGOP">∃</XMTok>
                      <XMApp>
                        <XMTok role="SUBSCRIPTOP" scriptpos="post2"/>
                        <XMTok font="italic" role="UNKNOWN">q</XMTok>
                        <XMTok font="italic" fontsize="70%" role="UNKNOWN">k</XMTok>
                      </XMApp>
                    </XMApp>
                  </XMApp>
                  <XMTok meaning="element-of" name="in" role="RELOP">∈</XMTok>
                  <XMApp>
                    <XMTok meaning="times" role="MULOP">⁢</XMTok>
                    <XMDual>
                      <XMApp>
                        <XMTok meaning="open-interval"/>
                        <XMRef idref="S0.E21.m1.7"/>
                        <XMRef idref="S0.E21.m1.8.1"/>
                      </XMApp>
                      <XMWrap>
                        <XMTok role="OPEN" stretchy="false">(</XMTok>
                        <XMTok meaning="0" role="NUMBER" xml:id="S0.E21.m1.7">0</XMTok>
                        <XMTok role="PUNCT">,</XMTok>
                        <XMApp xml:id="S0.E21.m1.8.1">
                          <XMTok meaning="divide" role="MULOP">/</XMTok>
                          <XMTok meaning="1" role="NUMBER">1</XMTok>
                          <XMTok font="italic" role="UNKNOWN">k</XMTok>
                        </XMApp>
                        <XMTok role="CLOSE" rpadding="5.0pt" stretchy="false">)</XMTok>
                      </XMWrap>

      <Math mode="display" tex="\begin{split}&amp;\displaystyle t_{j}^{2}\|\nabla\widehat{u}_{j}\|_{2}^{2}+m_{0}e^%&#10;{2\tilde{\theta}_{j}}\|\widehat{u}_{j}\|_{2}^{2}+3q_{j}^{2}\frac{e^{8\tilde{%&#10;\theta}_{j}}}{t_{j}^{6}}\varphi^{\prime}\Big{(}\frac{q_{j}e^{4\tilde{\theta}_{%&#10;j}}N(\widehat{u}_{j})}{t_{j}^{4}}\Big{)}N^{2}(\widehat{u}_{j})+3q_{j}\frac{e^{%&#10;4\tilde{\theta}_{j}}}{t_{j}^{2}}\varphi\Big{(}\frac{q_{j}e^{4\tilde{\theta}_{j%&#10;}}N(\widehat{u}_{j})}{t_{j}^{4}}\Big{)}N(\widehat{u}_{j})\\&#10;&amp;\displaystyle=e^{2\tilde{\theta}_{j}}\int_{\mathbb{R}^{2}}\Big{(}g(\widehat{u%&#10;}_{j})\widehat{u}_{j}+m_{0}(\widehat{u}_{j})^{2}\Big{)}\,dx+o_{j}(1){\leqslant%&#10;}e^{2\tilde{\theta}_{j}}\int_{\mathbb{R}^{2}}\lambda(\widehat{u}_{j})\widehat{%&#10;u}_{j}\,dx+o_{j}(1)\rightarrow 0.\end{split}" text="(t _ j) ^ 2 * ((norm@(nabla@((widehat@(u)) _ j))) _ 2) ^ 2 + m _ 0 * e ^ (2 * (tilde@(theta)) _ j) * ((norm@((widehat@(u)) _ j)) _ 2) ^ 2 + 3 * (q _ j) ^ 2 * (e ^ (8 * (tilde@(theta)) _ j) / (t _ j) ^ 6) * varphi ^ prime * ((q _ j * e ^ (4 * (tilde@(theta)) _ j) * N * (widehat@(u)) _ j) / (t _ j) ^ 4) * N ^ 2 * (widehat@(u)) _ j + 3 * q _ j * (e ^ (4 * (tilde@(theta)) _ j) / (t _ j) ^ 2) * varphi * ((q _ j * e ^ (4 * (tilde@(theta)) _ j) * N * (widehat@(u)) _ j) / (t _ j) ^ 4) * N * (widehat@(u)) _ j = e ^ (2 * (tilde@(theta)) _ j) * (integral _ (R ^ 2))@((g * (widehat@(u)) _ j * (widehat@(u)) _ j + m _ 0 * ((widehat@(u)) _ j) ^ 2) * differential-d@(x)) + o _ j * 1 less= e ^ (2 * (tilde@(theta)) _ j) * (integral _ (R ^ 2))@(lambda * (widehat@(u)) _ j * (widehat@(u)) _ j * differential-d@(x)) + o _ j * 1 rightarrow 0" xml:id="S0.E27.m1">

        <tag>(31)</tag>

        <tag role="refnum">31</tag>

      <Math mode="display" tex="\begin{split}&amp;\displaystyle\|\nabla{u}_{j}^{(n,q)}\|^{2}+m_{0}e^{2\theta_{j}^{%&#10;(n,q)}}\|u_{j}^{(n,q)}\|_{2}^{2}+\frac{q^{2}}{2}e^{8\theta_{j}^{(n,q)}}\varphi%&#10;^{\prime}\big{(}qe^{4\theta_{j}^{(n,q)}}N({u}_{j}^{(n,q)})\big{)}N({u}_{j}^{(n%&#10;,q)})N^{\prime}({u}_{j}^{(n,q)})[{u}_{j}^{(n,q)}]\\&#10;&amp;\displaystyle\quad+\frac{q}{2}e^{4\theta_{j}^{(n,q)}}\varphi\big{(}qe^{4%&#10;\theta_{j}^{(n,q)}}N({u}_{j}^{(n,q)})\big{)}N^{\prime}({u}_{j}^{(n,q)})[{u}_{j%&#10;}^{(n,q)}]\\&#10;&amp;\displaystyle=e^{2\theta_{j}^{(n,q)}}\int_{\mathbb{R}^{2}}\lambda(u_{j}^{(n,q%&#10;)})u_{j}^{(n,q)}\,dx-e^{2\theta_{j}^{(n,q)}}\int_{\mathbb{R}^{2}}\Big{(}%&#10;\lambda(u_{j}^{(n,q)})u_{j}^{(n,q)}-g({u}_{j}^{(n,q)}){u}_{j}^{(n,q)}-m_{0}(u_%&#10;{j}^{(n,q)})^{2}\Big{)}\,dx+o_{j}(1).\end{split}" text="(norm@(nabla@((u _ j) ^ (open-interval@(n, q))))) ^ 2 + m _ 0 * e ^ (2 * (theta _ j) ^ (open-interval@(n, q))) * ((norm@((u _ j) ^ (open-interval@(n, q)))) _ 2) ^ 2 + (q ^ 2 / 2) * e ^ (8 * (theta _ j) ^ (open-interval@(n, q))) * varphi ^ prime * q * e ^ (4 * (theta _ j) ^ (open-interval@(n, q))) * N * (u _ j) ^ (open-interval@(n, q)) * N * (u _ j) ^ (open-interval@(n, q)) * N ^ prime * (u _ j) ^ (open-interval@(n, q)) * delimited-[]@((u _ j) ^ (open-interval@(n, q))) + (q / 2) * e ^ (4 * (theta _ j) ^ (open-interval@(n, q))) * varphi * q * e ^ (4 * (theta _ j) ^ (open-interval@(n, q))) * N * (u _ j) ^ (open-interval@(n, q)) * N ^ prime * (u _ j) ^ (open-interval@(n, q)) * delimited-[]@((u _ j) ^ (open-interval@(n, q))) = (e ^ (2 * (theta _ j) ^ (open-interval@(n, q))) * (integral _ (R ^ 2))@(lambda * (u _ j) ^ (open-interval@(n, q)) * (u _ j) ^ (open-interval@(n, q)) * differential-d@(x)) -     <equation labels="LABEL:b4" xml:id="S0.E32">
      <tags>
        <tag>(32)</tag>
        <tag role="autoref">Equation 32</tag>
        <tag role="refnum">32</tag>
      </tags>
      <Math mode="display" tex="\begin{split}&amp;\displaystyle\liminf_{j\rightarrow\infty}\int_{\mathbb{R}^{2}}%&#10;\Big{(}\lambda(u_{j}^{(n,q)})u_{j}^{(n,q)}-m_{0}(u_{j}^{(n,q)})^{2}-g({u}_{j}^%&#10;{(n,q)}){u}_{j}^{(n,q)}\Big{)}\,dx\\&#10;&amp;\displaystyle\quad{\geqslant}\int_{\mathbb{R}^{2}}\Big{(}\lambda(u^{(n,q)})u^%&#10;{(n,q)}-m_{0}(u^{(n,q)})^{2}-g({u}^{(n,q)}){u}^{(n,q)}\Big{)}\,dx.\end{split}" text="(limit-infimum _ (j rightarrow infinity))@((integral _ (R ^ 2))@((lambda * (u _ j) ^ (open-interval@(n, q)) * (u _ j) ^ (open-interval@(n, q)) - m _ 0 * (u _ j) ^ (open-interval@(n, q)) ^ 2 - g * (u _ j) ^ (open-interval@(n, q)) * (u _ j) ^ (open-interval@(n, q))) * differential-d@(x))) &gt;= (integral _ (R ^ 2))@((lambda * u ^ (open-interval@(n, q)) * u ^ (open-interval@(n, q)) - m _ 0 * u ^ (open-interval@(n, q)) ^ 2 - g * u ^ (open-interval@(n, q)) * u ^ (open-interval@(n, q))) * differential-d@(x))" xml:id="S0.E32.m1">

        <MathFork>
          <Math tex="\displaystyle\limsup_{j\rightarrow\infty}\|u_{j}^{(n,q)}\|^{2}=\limsup_{j%&#10;\rightarrow\infty}\Big{[}-\frac{q^{2}}{2}e^{8\theta_{j}^{(n,q)}}\varphi^{%&#10;\prime}\big{(}qe^{4\theta_{j}^{(n,q)}}N({u}_{j}^{(n,q)})\big{)}N({u}_{j}^{(n,q%&#10;)})N^{\prime}({u}_{j}^{(n,q)})[{u}_{j}^{(n,q)}]" xml:id="S0.Ex78.m3">
            <XMath>
              <XMApp scriptpos="mid">
                <XMTok role="SUBSCRIPTOP" scriptpos="mid8"/>
                <XMTok meaning="limit-supremum" name="limsup" role="LIMITOP" scriptpos="mid">lim sup</XMTok>
                <XMApp>
                  <XMTok fontsize="70%" name="rightarrow" role="ARROW">→</XMTok>
                  <XMTok font="italic" fontsize="70%" role="UNKNOWN">j</XMTok>
                  <XMTok fontsize="70%" meaning="infinity" name="infty" role="ID">∞</XMTok>
                </XMApp>
              </XMApp>
              <XMTok meaning="parallel-to" name="||" role="VERTBAR">∥</XMTok>
              <XMApp>
                <XMTok role="SUPERSCRIPTOP" scriptpos="post8"/>
                <XMApp>
                  <XMTok role="SUBSCRIPTOP" scriptpos="post8"/>
                  <XMTok font="italic" role="UNKNOWN">u</XMTok>
                  <XMTok font="italic" fontsize="70%" role="UNKNOWN">j</XMTok>
                </XMApp>

          <Math tex="\displaystyle=\|u^{(n,q)}\|^{2}." text="absent = (norm@(u ^ (open-interval@(n, q)))) ^ 2" xml:id="S0.Ex83.m3">
